苯丙氨酸羟化酶是体内过量苯丙氨酸[[分解代谢|分解代谢]]的[[限速步骤|限速]]酶。Seymour Kaufman关于苯丙氨酸羟化酶的研究使一种新的生物辅酶'''四氢生物蝶呤'''被发现。<ref name="pmid13525410">{{cite journal | author = KAUFMAN S | title = A new cofactor required for the enzymatic conversion of phenylalanine to tyrosine | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 230 | issue = 2 | pages = 931–9 | pmid = 13525410 | doi = |date=February 1958}}</ref> 此酶受到人类健康方面的关注是因为编码该酶的''PAH''基因如果发生突变，会造成严重的代谢紊乱即[[苯丙酮尿症|苯丙酮尿症]]

== 酶反应机制 ==

反应认为是按照以下步骤进行：

# 形成 Fe(II)-O-O-BH<sub>4</sub> 桥.
# O-O键异裂产生铁氧羟化中间体 Fe(IV)=O.
# attack on Fe(IV)=O to hydroxylate phenylalanine substrate to tyrosine.<ref name="Fitzpatrick_2003">{{cite journal | author = Fitzpatrick PF | title = Mechanism of aromatic amino acid hydroxylation | journal = Biochemistry | volume = 42 | issue = 48 | pages = 14083–91 | pmid = 14640675 | pmc = 1635487 | doi = 10.1021/bi035656u |date=December 2003}}</ref>

